#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:2 a7acf6b869774118845670dbe17a59f1
msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "变更日志"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:4 87795de3fd124734bfdfca0f2b181904
msgid ""
"This page documents **developer-visible** changes across VoxCPM releases — "
"new APIs, architecture flags, CLI commands, config fields, training script "
"updates, and dependency changes. If you are migrating between versions, read"
" from your current version forward."
msgstr ""
"本页记录各版 VoxCPM **对开发者可见** 的变更——新 "
"API、架构标记、CLI、配置字段、训练脚本与依赖。若在版本间迁移，请从你当前版本往后阅读。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:12 59f4e212645f4935a8a15844e39ba22c
msgid "VoxCPM 2.0 — March 2026"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2.0 — 2026 年 3 月"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:16 ff55099cbf004d1dacf83d60373265e9
msgid "**Breaking changes at a glance** — read before upgrading from 1.x:"
msgstr "**破坏性变更一览** — 从 1.x 升级前请先读："

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:18 3b14c1ff25224933a9632a09fb0e9ec9
msgid ""
"``VoxCPM.from_pretrained()`` now defaults to ``openbmb/VoxCPM2``. If you "
"rely on the default, your code will load the 2B model instead of VoxCPM 1.5."
" Pin explicitly if needed: "
"``VoxCPM.from_pretrained(\"openbmb/VoxCPM1.5\")``."
msgstr ""
"``VoxCPM.from_pretrained()`` 现默认 `` openbmb/VoxCPM2``。若依赖默认行为，代码会加载 2B 模型而非 "
"VoxCPM 1.5。需要时请显式固定：`` VoxCPM.from_pretrained(\"openbmb/VoxCPM1.5\")``。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:23 6caf3814c52b4c97abb1299a6dc8d18c
msgid ""
"**Output sample rate changed**: 44.1 kHz (1.5) → **48 kHz** (2.0). Any code "
"that hard-codes ``sf.write(..., 44100)`` must switch to "
"``model.tts_model.sample_rate`` (which returns ``48000`` for V2)."
msgstr ""
"**输出采样率变更**：44.1 kHz（1.5）→ ** 48 kHz** （2.0）。凡硬编码 ``sf.write(..., 44100)`` "
"的代码须改为 `` model.tts_model.sample_rate`` （V2 返回 `` 48000``）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:27 4471f70dd4af4cf48a5f8b988496eef7
msgid ""
"**Gradio** dependency bumped to ``>=6,<7``. Gradio 5 apps will not install "
"alongside VoxCPM 2. ``app_old.py`` (the 1.5 demo) has been adapted to Gradio"
" 6 as well."
msgstr ""
"**Gradio** 依赖升至 ``>=6,<7``。Gradio 5 应用无法与 VoxCPM 2 并存安装。`` app_old.py`` （1.5"
" Demo）也已适配 Gradio 6。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:31 ac66b3597e864019b360595971353e70
msgid ""
"**CLI subcommand design**: the old flat ``voxcpm --text ...`` still works "
"but prints a deprecation warning. Prefer ``voxcpm design|clone|batch``."
msgstr ""
"**CLI 子命令设计**：旧式扁平 ``voxcpm --text ...`` 仍可用，但会打印弃用警告。请优先使用 `` voxcpm "
"design|clone|batch``。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:37 a624972782a64cff9d68d099eb0b5cd1
msgid "30-Language Multilingual"
msgstr "30 种语言多语"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:39 b68ee60dd33746939ced505726ee7b2e
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 2 extends language support from **2 (Chinese, English)** to **30 "
"languages** across 8 language families, trained on 2.36 million hours of "
"data (1.8M zh+en base + 560K multilingual). The full language list is "
"documented in :doc:`../models/voxcpm2`."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 2 将语言支持从 **2 种（中、英）** 扩展到 ** 30 种语言**、8 个语系，训练数据约 236 万小时（180 万小时中英基础"
" + 56 万小时多语）。完整列表见 :doc:`../models/voxcpm2`。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:44 8672f52a82de4a819626f15ae3f0869f
msgid ""
"At the code level, multilingual synthesis requires **no API changes** — "
"simply pass text in any supported language. Language detection is handled "
"internally by the model."
msgstr "在代码层面，多语合成 **无需改 API** —— 直接传入任意支持语言的文本即可，语言检测由模型内部完成。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:50 ../../reference/changelog.rst:465
#: 3164f60fb690440597afb393a01f4735 621289b6fa9d47b3b466ca549d988c58
msgid "Model & Architecture"
msgstr "模型与架构"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:52 2e336a986faf4bc4abe5b96460489512
msgid ""
"**New model class** ``VoxCPM2Model`` (``model/voxcpm2.py``). Existing "
"``VoxCPMModel`` (``model/voxcpm.py``) is unchanged and continues to serve "
"1.0 / 1.5 checkpoints."
msgstr ""
"**新模型类** ``VoxCPM2Model`` （`` model/voxcpm2.py``）。既有 `` VoxCPMModel`` （`` "
"model/voxcpm.py``）不变，继续服务 1.0 / 1.5 检查点。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:56 e3c9497cc75c4813baed682ab7a312bf
msgid ""
"**Architecture auto-detection** via ``config.json`` → ``\"architecture\"`` "
"field:"
msgstr "**架构自动检测**：通过 ``config.json`` 的 ``\"architecture\"`` 字段："

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:58 32a54980a9eb4b49b46b2f3b81658bd7
msgid "``\"voxcpm2\"`` → ``VoxCPM2Model``"
msgstr "``\"voxcpm2\"`` → `` VoxCPM2Model``"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:59 57b7a1796c5e402b901faebf77cbe66d
msgid "``\"voxcpm\"`` (or key absent) → ``VoxCPMModel``"
msgstr "``\"voxcpm\"`` （或缺省）→ `` VoxCPMModel``"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:61 fe518a1a3e0242c38e61ad69556686c3
msgid "**Parameter count**: 2B (up from 750M in 1.5)."
msgstr "**参数量**：2B（1.5 为 750M）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:63 0aafc1a3999f4deb8c9084ebc3a8f44e
msgid ""
"**Residual LM fusion**: additive → concat-projection. New "
"``fusion_concat_proj`` linear layer (``Linear(2h → h)``)."
msgstr ""
"**残差 LM 融合**：由加性改为拼接投影。新增 ``fusion_concat_proj`` 线性层（`` Linear(2h → h)``）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:74 75a23bf6182445e7ac7e88a2b14e4ff0
msgid ""
"**DiT conditioning**: single-token add → multi-token concat. "
"``VoxCPMLocDiTV2`` (``modules/locdit/local_dit_v2.py``) reshapes the "
"concatenated LM + residual projections into multiple prefix tokens."
msgstr ""
"**DiT 条件**：单 token 相加 → 多 token 拼接。``VoxCPMLocDiTV2`` （`` "
"modules/locdit/local_dit_v2.py``）将拼接后的 LM + 残差投影重塑为多个前缀 token。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:86 434a69ef55994338b791a2ce390dbf90
msgid ""
"**Isolated reference audio channel** with special tokens "
"``ref_audio_start_token = 103``, ``ref_audio_end_token = 104``. Enables four"
" generation modes: zero-shot, continuation, reference-only, combined (ref + "
"continuation)."
msgstr ""
"**独立参考音频通道**，特殊 token ``ref_audio_start_token = 103``、`` ref_audio_end_token"
" = 104``。支持四种生成模式：zero-shot、continuation、reference-only、combined（参考 + 延续）。"

