#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:467 d8357731d2fd4f529eb8ca164dbebd7b
msgid ""
"**AudioVAE sampling rate**: 16 kHz → **44.1 kHz**. Preserves more high-"
"frequency detail for voice cloning."
msgstr "**AudioVAE 采样率**：16 kHz → ** 44.1 kHz**。保留更多高频细节，利于声音克隆。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:470 5dad55336cbc485c9c734fc0c97bf2de
msgid ""
"**LM token rate**: 12.5 Hz → **6.25 Hz** (halved). Reduces computational "
"cost per second of audio."
msgstr "**LM token 率**：12.5 Hz → ** 6.25 Hz** （减半）。降低每秒音频的计算量。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:473 2304d7aed42f4e3ba6c694add97f5f40
msgid ""
"**Patch size**: 2 → **4** (LocEnc & LocDiT). Encoder/decoder process longer "
"patches, requiring deeper local modules → slightly larger total parameter "
"count (**~750M**)."
msgstr ""
"**Patch size**：2 → ** 4** （LocEnc 与 LocDiT）。编解码处理更长 patch，需要更深的局部模块 → "
"总参数量略增（** 约 750M**）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:477 dfda5ed9c7ed4fa189f948010bfcacf9
msgid "**RTF**: ~0.15 on RTX 4090 (comparable to 1.0 despite larger model)."
msgstr "**RTF**：RTX 4090 上约 0.15（尽管模型更大，与 1.0 相当）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:479 c14aeb2b1c184e10b6372ba0be9d5d2d
msgid ""
"**config.json** ``architecture`` value: ``\"voxcpm\"`` (same code path as "
"1.0)."
msgstr "**config.json** 中 ``architecture`` 取值：``\"voxcpm\"`` （与 1.0 同一代码路径）。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:482 c1bccd66a9f2442f979b17d840e3f1d9
msgid ""
"Same model class ``VoxCPMModel`` as 1.0. All 1.0 → 1.5 differences are in "
"checkpoint weights and config values, **not** in a separate Python class."
msgstr ""
"与 1.0 使用同一模型类 ``VoxCPMModel``。1.0 → 1.5 的差异在检查点权重与配置值，**并非** 单独 Python 类。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:488 36acb8d42d5340e9abe6e9804c723076
msgid "Fine-tuning"
msgstr "微调"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:490 4db6878d5d0b496e857823df5f6e2c8e
msgid ""
"**SFT** (full fine-tuning) and **LoRA** fine-tuning officially supported."
msgstr "正式支持 **SFT** （全参微调）与 ** LoRA** 微调。"

#: ../../reference/changelog.rst:492 7141100960ec4920a4767bb4f9869999
msgid "**Training script** ``scripts/train_voxcpm_finetune.py`` added."
